  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Respond and Meet the Most Urgent Food Needs in the Conflict-Affected Area of Donetsk NGCA</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To ensure food security for affected by the ongoing conflict, IOM is providing food parcels to approximately 3,500 households. In order to ensure rapid response, IOM will proceed with local procurement performed though local non-governmental organisations authorized to implement in the area, thus minimizing the risk of impeded crossing of the line of control and securing soonest delivery.</narrative>
  </description>
